comment: /**  * Get an element given its index.  */
code: /**  * Get an element given its index.  */ int get(long index).

comment: /**  * Set a value at the given index and return the previous value.  */
code: /**  * Set a value at the given index and return the previous value.  */ int set(long index, int value).

comment: /** * Increment value at the given index by inc and return the value. */
code: /** * Increment value at the given index by inc and return the value. */ int increment(long index, int inc).

comment: /** * Fill slots between fromIndex inclusive to toIndex exclusive with value. */
code: /** * Fill slots between fromIndex inclusive to toIndex exclusive with value. */ void fill(long fromIndex, long toIndex, int value).
